          "text": "Theorem. For an integer n, n is even if and only if n^2 is even.\n\nProof. For the forward direction, if n=2k then n^2=2(2k^2), so n^2 is even. For the reverse direction, use the contrapositive: if n is odd, then n^2 is odd.",
